  "3290660": {
    "name": "Pirate Cove Simulator",
    "steam_appid": 3290660,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就算是最幸运的海盗，运气也总有用完的时候！在<strong>Pirate Cove Simulator</strong>中，你是一支海盗船队的船长，在满载宝藏返航时遭遇了一场猛烈的风暴。你在传说中的诅咒之岛上醒来，这里是所有最优秀的海盗在海上丧生后的归宿。你死了，你的水手们也都死了！但事情不一定要这样继续下去。也许你能用钱买到离开这个地方的机会...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🏴‍☠️<strong><u>与亡灵做生意</u></strong>🏴‍☠️</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290660/extras/8639200be4ad379fee40cc90f4e66072.poster.avif?t=1761218085\" width=618 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290660/extras/8639200be4ad379fee40cc90f4e66072.webm?t=1761218085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290660/extras/8639200be4ad379fee40cc90f4e66072.mp4?t=1761218085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >诅咒之岛上到处都是亡灵海盗...而且碰巧他们都有很多金币！开一家商店和酒馆似乎是帮助他们摆脱不再需要的财富的好方法，也可能给你一个买路离开这个地方的机会。补充货架，设定价格，通过交易赚取你的金币！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🏴‍☠️<strong><u>经营你自己的酿酒厂</u></strong>🏴‍☠️</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290660/extras/e90db84293f1f4bd506d3fbe355be66e.poster.avif?t=1761218085\" width=618 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290660/extras/e90db84293f1f4bd506d3fbe355be66e.webm?t=1761218085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290660/extras/e90db84293f1f4bd506d3fbe355be66e.mp4?t=1761218085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为什么诅咒之岛上的朗姆酒总是不够？亡灵们无法操作酿酒厂。是时候改变这一切了！混合当地的植物来找到完美的口感，为那些不安分的海盗灵魂蒸馏烈酒。找到你自己喜欢的配方。当然，他们喝的所有东西都会从骨头里漏出来洒在地上，但重要的是 - 他们会回来再买一轮！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🏴‍☠️<strong><u>...或者就去钓鱼</u></strong>🏴‍☠️</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290660/extras/6a4d6eaa206ea6187295f6371ea9aa79.poster.avif?t=1761218085\" width=618 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290660/extras/6a4d6eaa206ea6187295f6371ea9aa79.webm?t=1761218085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290660/extras/6a4d6eaa206ea6187295f6371ea9aa79.mp4?t=1761218085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏充满了远超标准休闲经济模拟游戏的活动。在酿酒厂工作、补充货架、交易商品很有趣，但这些都是你的船员可以代劳的。这让你可以自由地在岛上漫步和探索，寻找稀有植物，寻找埋藏的宝藏，或者就是去钓鱼！有些活动能帮你赚取金币以买路离开冥界，有些则不能。但它们都很有趣！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290660/extras/52fbc6c648d9a31b591bd9a1408154ff.poster.avif?t=1761218085\" width=618 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290660/extras/52fbc6c648d9a31b591bd9a1408154ff.webm?t=1761218085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290660/extras/52fbc6c648d9a31b591bd9a1408154ff.mp4?t=1761218085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🏴‍☠️<strong><u>啊哈！快加入愿望单，水手！</u></strong>🏴‍☠️</h2>",
